Immerse yourself in the world of VAIL, a multiplayer FPS game built for virtual reality. Engage in high-octane gameplay centered around objective-based game modes or connect with a vibrant community in social environments. Set in a sci-fi future of the solar system, choose between opposing factions and battle for the claim to humanityâ€™s legacy.
{390905377282488}

#  **EXPERIENCE UNPARALLELED COMBAT**

Feel high-impact FPS combat with best-in-class shooter mechanics, precisely tuned interactions, and immersive physics systems.

{1162628724924512}

# **LEVEL UP AND UNLOCK REWARDS**

Dominate in popular team-based and free-for-all game modes as you level up, unlock rewards, and top the leaderboards.

{766149719046755}

#  **UNCOVER VAIL'S STORY**
Traverse through awe-inspiring brutalist environments as the lines between right and wrong begin to blur.


{1884336785321853}

# **YOUR NEXT BEST FRIEND IS ONE REALITY AWAY**

Unite with your friends for battle, or bring them to your Armory to play mini-games and chill.

{1136583027611274}

